1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 25=

3
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,440
Qingyao,

4
00:00:46,470 --> 00:00:47,310
don't worry,

5
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:51,200
everything will settle soon.

6
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:52,400
My Lord!

7
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:54,630
My Lord.

8
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:01,560
My Lord, something's wrong!

9
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,520
Please.

10
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,320
It's you.

11
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:37,840
How did it go?

12
00:01:39,150 --> 00:01:40,120
No answer yet.

13
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:46,400
Don't lose heart.

14
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,070
Your father's been acting mysteriously
lately.

15
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,150
He must be meeting someone important.

16
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,510
Perhaps,

17
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,790
he's plotting something
against the throne.

18
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,320
Let's go.

19
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:20,150
There are so many people here today.

20
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,190
How dare you show up here?

21
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,660
Ling Yu is right here in the manor.

22
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:23,960
If he discovers us,

23
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,590
we both will lose our heads.

24
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:27,560
If you hadn't stalled for so long,

25
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,400
do you think I wanted to come?

26
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:31,400
If you can't bring yourself to kill her,

27
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:34,120
then I'll do it for you.

28
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,960
Don't you dare.

29
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,680
Qingyao is the only child
whom Yulian and I have.

30
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,520
I never meant to drag her into this.

31
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,680
Besides, she's carrying a child now.

32
00:02:45,050 --> 00:02:46,330
I won't allow you to touch her.

33
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,800
Gu Pingzhang,

34
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,520
when that old man

35
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,280
killed Zhou Yulian back then,

36
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:57,360
who swore to make him pay double?

37
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,910
This is the perfect moment.

38
00:03:00,690 --> 00:03:01,950
Will you just stand by and watch

39
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,010
his son take the throne

40
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:04,800
and forever hold power over you?

41
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,800
But Qingyao is innocent.

42
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,560
There must be a way
to handle this wisely.

43
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,400
Hmph.

44
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:16,240
Back then, you nearly

45
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,960
strangled that child to death.

46
00:03:19,650 --> 00:03:21,350
And now you pretend
to be a caring father?

47
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:23,870
It's still unknown whose child
Gu Qingyao really is.

48
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:25,590
Qingyao is, of course, my child.

49
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:26,720
So what?

50
00:03:28,060 --> 00:03:30,460
Do you just want to win over him easily

51
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:32,180
without paying any price?

52
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:34,180
In the end,

53
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:38,020
I'm the one left with nothing.

54
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:45,540
Gu Pingzhang,

55
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,140
don't you forget

56
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,540
that all these years,

57
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:52,900
your rise to prime minister
was built on my sacrifices.

58
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:00,420
All these years,

59
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:03,420
I've indeed failed you.

60
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:06,300
But you cannot use Qingyao's life
to make amends.

61
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:10,700
You failed me?

62
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:12,980
Easy for you to say.

63
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:14,820
Back then,

64
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:19,500
your virtuous mother,

65
00:04:20,420 --> 00:04:22,620
because of a fortune teller's words,

66
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:27,580
feared I would bring misfortune
to her precious son,

67
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:31,820
and cast me off to a peasant family,

68
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,820
left me to live or die on my own.

69
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:38,540
We were born of the same mother,

70
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,340
so why is it that you became

71
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:44,740
a high and mighty minister of power,

72
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:51,020
while I was raised
as a servant by a farmer?

73
00:04:58,820 --> 00:04:59,660
Do you have any idea

74
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,100
how hard it is for a woman
without a mother

75
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,980
to survive in the imperial harem?

76
00:05:06,420 --> 00:05:07,500
If not for that,

77
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,090
Huan would never have been harmed

78
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:10,420
even before he was born,

79
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,900
and frail since his earliest days.

80
00:05:18,980 --> 00:05:19,980
Gu Pingzhang,

81
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,940
all of this is what you owe me.

82
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,140
Aren't you reluctant to kill her?

83
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,540
Fine.

84
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:30,340
Then trade it with your heart's blood.

85
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:35,980
Alright.

86
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,220
Let me think about it.

87
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,140
Brother,

88
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:44,500
haven't you already made up your mind?

89
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:47,460
From the moment you sent her
into the Crown Prince's Residence,

90
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:49,460
there's been no turning back for us.

91
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:55,020
Brother,

92
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,180
do you really think

93
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:58,940
that when Ling Yu takes power,

94
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,340
he'll let you stand beside him
as his equal?

95
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:03,220
If he ascends the throne,

96
00:06:03,540 --> 00:06:05,300
the first person he'll remove is you.

97
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:07,100
But if Huan were the one instead,

98
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:08,700
everything would be different.

99
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,660
Huan is still young.

100
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:20,020
Naturally, matters of state
would fall under your control.

101
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,420
I'm only his uncle.

102
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:26,540
No.

103
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,740
You're not just his uncle.

104
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,820
In my eyes and Huan's eyes,

105
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:33,300
you're no different

106
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:34,380
from his own father.

107
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:45,220
Only in this way,

108
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,420
can you step over his son's head,

109
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,300
and ascend the throne.

110
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,840
That would be the finest revenge
against him.

111
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,700
Only then will Yulian rest in peace

112
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,340
in the underworld.

113
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:03,060
Fine.

114
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:08,250
I'll do as you say.

115
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,340
Qingyao,

116
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,330
after all these years,
you've not changed at all.

117
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:04,520
You're still that tearful girl
from back then.

118
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:11,140
Qingyao,

119
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,620
the world has always been cruel.

120
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,100
The only ones we can rely on

121
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:19,660
are ourselves.

122
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:23,300
My Lord,

123
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:25,600
there's a promising young talent
from the Northern Desert.

124
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:27,780
Though she's a bit older.

125
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:37,980
Age doesn't matter.

126
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:42,820
What matters is potential.

127
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,220
From now on, you'll be called Lingsan.

128
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:49,300
Yes.

129
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,480
Father, Father.

130
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:52,660
Yao.

131
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,820
Father, Father.

132
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:57,220
Will you play with me?

133
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,060
Don't you see I'm handling
important affairs?

134
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:00,820
Father, I'm so bored.

135
00:09:00,820 --> 00:09:03,740
Can we play hide-and-seek, father?

136
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:04,820
- Steward.
- Here.

137
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,060
- Take her away.
- Yes.

138
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:07,580
- Play with me.
- My Lady.

139
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:10,540
Let go of me! Let go!

140
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:13,300
Release me!

141
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,300
From now on, without my permission,

142
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,780
do not bring them to be here.

143
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:20,820
Yes.

144
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:28,300
Mother,

145
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:31,580
my father doesn't like me anymore.

146
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:34,620
A grown child still cries like that.

147
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,260
Mind your own business.

148
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,180
You're just a child yourself.

149
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,300
We may be close in age,

150
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,460
but our lives

151
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:45,700
are worlds apart.

152
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:48,420
Stop putting on an adult's air.

153
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:50,420
What's so different about you?

154
00:09:50,810 --> 00:09:52,340
You were born into a good family,

155
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,050
enjoying a carefree life
in fine clothes.

156
00:09:54,330 --> 00:09:56,060
So when things don't go your way,

157
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:57,260
you cry like a child.

158
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,860
I was born an orphan,

159
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:01,140
and all my pain

160
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:03,580
can only be swallowed inside me.

161
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:05,260
Where are your parents?

162
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:11,340
I don't remember.

163
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:12,740
That's all right.

164
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,500
I'll be your friend.

165
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,020
No, thank you.

166
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,380
We walk different paths.

167
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:39,780
I hate you.

168
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:44,220
The world has always been cruel.

169
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,500
The only ones we can rely on

170
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:48,820
are ourselves.

171
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,180
It's you.

172
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,330
No matter how harsh this world is,

173
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:08,380
I'll fight back with you.

174
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,540
Even through blades and fire,

175
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:14,260
or to the ends of the earth,

176
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,540
I'll stay by your side.

177
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:43,940
Will you be my friend?

178
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:48,300
Yes, I will.

179
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,380
Qingyao,

180
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:47,620
you're back.

181
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:52,140
Your Highness, what troubles you so?

182
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,640
Why are you drinking alone in my room

183
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:56,380
brooding over your thoughts?

184
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:59,340
My father's health is worsening.

185
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:00,740
The imperial physician said

186
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,300
he won't hold on much longer.

187
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,060
In that case,

188
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,370
you should prioritize your health
even more.

189
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:13,620
His illness isn't caused
by natural sickness.

190
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:18,700
I suspect someone has poisoned him.

191
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:23,460
Who would dare to do that?

192
00:13:24,340 --> 00:13:25,340
I do not know yet.

193
00:13:26,100 --> 00:13:28,060
My father has lived
without great merit or fault.

194
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:30,340
But it is this gentle nature

195
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:32,620
that invited those with greedy hearts.

196
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:34,300
Now,

197
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:38,140
this heavy burden falls upon me.

198
00:13:39,580 --> 00:13:41,420
Your Highness, do you fear

199
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:42,900
you may not govern the realm well?

200
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:46,980
Do you think I can, Qingyao?

201
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:51,820
You are gracious and humble,

202
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:53,190
yet hides your strength from view.

203
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:55,860
Of course, you can.

204
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:59,140
Turns out you think so highly of me.

205
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:03,460
Your Highness,

206
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,980
will you become a wise ruler?

207
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:24,340
I cannot say.

208
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,100
The achievements of a lifetime

209
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,740
is for future generations to judge.

210
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:32,660
Enough.

211
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,920
Let's leave this talk aside.

212
00:14:34,340 --> 00:14:36,260
Here, share a drink.

213
00:15:06,340 --> 00:15:08,940
♪When a breeze passes by♪

214
00:15:09,460 --> 00:15:12,780
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

215
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:15,420
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

216
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:18,900
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

217
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:22,220
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

218
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:25,540
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

219
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:28,460
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

220
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:32,260
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

221
00:15:32,420 --> 00:15:34,020
♪I finally understood that truth♪

222
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:35,500
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

223
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:37,340
♪I lose my way in the night♪

224
00:15:37,340 --> 00:15:38,820
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

225
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:40,500
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

226
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,460
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

227
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:46,340
♪For you and me to meet again♪

228
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:49,620
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

229
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,980
♪In the pouring rain♪

230
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:56,340
♪As if you are still by my side♪
